show.description:
A billionaire hiding as a beggar crosses paths with a simple girl bound by dreams, kindness, and fate.
What begins as a contract marriage to fulfill a grandmother’s dying wish turns into a journey of love and betrayal.
Will truth and destiny bring their hearts together—or tear them apart forever?
